Simulator for GraVF using verilator-generated C++ for user kernels

If using migen kernels:
> cd sim
> python3 ../src/sim_export_apply_scatter_kernels.py #(uses config.ini in current directory)

Otherwise, name kernel files ${APP}_apply.v and ${APP}_scatter.v and move to folder "sim".

Verilate:
> verilator -Wno-lint -Wno-INITIALDLY -Wno-COMBDLY --cc ${APP}_apply.v
> verilator -Wno-lint -Wno-INITIALDLY -Wno-COMBDLY --cc ${APP}_scatter.v

(creates folder "obj_dir")

> cd obj_dir
> make -f ../Makefile
> ./sim_main
